<D>__{a cemetery. how 'bout you coming with us?}
<C>__{nikki }
<D>__{no. i'm going with cary.}
<C>__{shep}
<P>__{(concerned)}
<D>__{you've been invited?}
<A>__{nikki appears in the doorway, dressed to go out.}
<C>__{nikki}
<D>__{do you think cary might object?}
