<D>__{well, cary likes to be alone. he's as brittle as a breadstick. one silly crack from you and he might break up in sections.}
<C>__{nikki}
<P>__{(thinks about this)}
<D>__{well, then, i don't think he should be left alone.}
<P>__{(beat)}
